snippet.title: MAJOR autumn update starts Sep 12th! | Curse of the Wandering Flames
snippet.description:
The major autumn update, Curse of the Wandering Flames, is here!

▶ Hunt Magnamalo, Rajang, and Aknosom, and wield your very own heavy bowgun!
▶ Get ready to cook with the beloved cooking feature from the Monster Hunter series! Hone your cooking skills and whip up the perfect Well-Done Steak to start your next hunt with a full Special Gauge 🍖

The hunt continues this autumn!

*You may need to restart your app to receive the update.
*Check the official website for details about the update.

Official website:
https://monsterhunternow.com/

Keep up with all the latest news on our social channels:
X:https://x.com/mh_now_en　
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mh_now_en/
